WEBVTT

00:03:57.793 --> 00:04:00.415
[Ishlashning ayni vaqti.] 
[Yo'q!]

00:04:00.439 --> 00:04:03.372
Ratsional inson ratsional qarorlar 
chiqaradi.

00:04:03.396 --> 00:04:05.292
Unumli ishlash...

00:04:05.316 --> 00:04:07.266
Lekin maymunchaga bu reja yoqmaydi.

00:04:07.290 --> 00:04:08.798
U shturvalni o'z qo'liga oladi

00:04:08.822 --> 00:04:11.703
va shunday deydi: "Yaxshisi, Vikipediyani 
o'qiymiz,

00:04:11.727 --> 00:04:13.863
Nensi Kerrigan va Tonya Harding 
mojarolari,

00:04:13.887 --> 00:04:16.018
negadir birdan ular esimga tushib qoldi".

00:04:16.042 --> 00:04:17.058
(Kulgu)

00:04:17.082 --> 00:04:18.240
Keyin...

00:04:18.264 --> 00:04:19.527
(Kulgu)

00:04:19.551 --> 00:04:21.589
Keyin biz muzlatgich yoniga boramiz,

00:04:21.613 --> 00:04:24.479
xuddi oxirgi 10 daqiqa ichida u yerda 
nimadir o'zgargandek.

00:04:24.503 --> 00:04:27.141
Keyin esa bizni YouTube girdobiga tortib 
ketadi:

00:04:27.165 --> 00:04:30.415
Richard Faynmanning magnitlar haqidagi 
suhbatidan boshlaymiz,